Items.c: <[>嘿,想不到我憑空多了個弟弟。這孩子這麼相信我,我可不能讓他被摩尼教的人抓走了,說什麼都要保護他。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Hey, I can't believe I have a brother out of nowhere. This kid trusts me so much, I can't let him be captured by the Manicheans, I have to protect him no matter what. <]>
